{"body": "This could lead to serious security holes since active record validations and callbacks to do not reference the correct association.\r\n\r\nFor example a web form updates super_admin_id on NuclearPlant model\r\n\r\nIn Nuclear Plan:\r\n\r\n    after_save do |u|\r\n      transfer_self_destruct_access_to super_admin\r\n    end\r\n\r\nWhoops! The old admin still has self destruct access and the new one doesn't. Old admin was fired for connections to terrorist organization, discovers he can still access self destruct. New admin doesn't have admin privileges. It's 3am. Everyone is sleeping. Boom.\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5080327", "created_at": "2012-04-11T22:12:24Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5818#issuecomment-5080327", "updated_at": "2012-04-11T22:13:58Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5818, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/crystalneth", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/de7a86a4af65781e3c4579161312bb60?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F930e465b24e652636d37b7aaa3ca92f1.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/received_events", "gravatar_id": "de7a86a4af65781e3c4579161312bb60", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "crystalneth", "type": "User", "id": 25253, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/crystalneth/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52381283bd3543c15100d984"}, "id": 50